articles.title: Sky Harbour Group Announces an Expansion to its Future New York Stewart International Airport Hangar Campus
articles.mainIdea: Sky Harbour Group Announces an Expansion to its Future New York Stewart International Airport Hangar Campus
articles.summary: Business Wire: Sky Harbour Group Announces an Expansion to its Future New York Stewart International Airport Hangar Campus. WEST HARRISON, N.Y., December 22, 2025--Sky Harbour Group Corporation (NYSE: SKYH, SKYH WS) ("SHG" or the "Company") today announced that the Port Authority of New York and New Jersey (PANYNJ) has authorized the execution of a lease amendment to expand Sky Harbour’s development site at New York Stewart International Airport (SWF) from 16 acres to 26 acres.
